ed from his last run. Overdue and is among the main hopes. 1. LITTLE RAT recorded her best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 7 length second behind Indy Melmen in 30.21. Has the ability and can measure up. 5. TASTE can measure up with the right run.\",\"runners\":[8,2,1,5],\"exclusive\":false}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,5,7]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,2,5,1]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,7,5,8]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,2,5,1]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,2,1,5]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,2,5,1]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,8,5,1]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}},{"wageringProduct":"EarlyQuaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"MEA","raceType":"G"}}]}}}